premise_source_doc_sentence: Margot Betty Frank  (  February 16 , 1926 -- February 1945  )  was the eldest daughter of Otto Frank and Edith Frank and the older sister of Anne Frank .

claim: Margot Frank was Anne Frank's teacher.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Hermine Santruschitz  (  15 February 1909 -- 11 January 2010  )  , better known as Miep Gies  (  -LSB- ˈmip ˈxis -RSB-  )  , was one of the Dutch citizens who hid Anne Frank , her family  (  Otto Frank , Margot Frank , Edith Frank-Holländer  )  and four other Jews  (  Fritz Pfeffer , Hermann van Pels , Auguste van Pels , Peter van Pels  )  from the Nazis in an annex above Anne 's father 's business premises during World War II .
